	<td>
		
			<font face="verdana" size="3" color="#9f3215"><b>    Into the Firepots -The Ancient Mystery</b></font>
			<br>
			<font face="verdana" size="2" color="#9f3215">
			<b><A href="mailto:xanthus@everlore.com">Xanthus</a></b></font>
			<font face="verdana" size="1" color="black">[04/25/2000 11:11:26 AM]</font><br>
		<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
			
		<blockquote>
<i><p>
The explorers found 4 strange spires sticking out of the water far out in the great ocean. After investigating they discovered that there was a room at the bottom of the spires on the ocean floor. They swam through the hole in the top, which apparently the room was not filled with water but breathable air. Looking around they discovered 12 firepots each with a different design. They resembled architectural designs of various major cities around Norrath. The discovery has been made. They tested each one being teleported to various locations all over Norrath, making down which firepots went where.</p>
<p>
They then used the firepots to return to their home towns and report their great discovery.</p></i>
<p>
/ooc: The firepots are teleporters to 12 major cities around Norrath. Be aware that you can teleport into a city where you are not liked and be in a world of hurt. However it appears that you will get ported near the zone line on all major cities. Special thanks to Golgorn for helping and Baelish of <a href="http://eq.castersrealm.com">Caster's Realm</a> for making the inital discovery. Here is a listing of all the firepot pictures. I will leave the location up to you :)</p>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://www.everlore.com/ShowScreenShot.asp?image=http://www.everlore.com/files/firepot12.jpg">Firepot: Freeport</a>
<li><a href="http://www.everlore.com/ShowScreenShot.asp?image=http://www.everlore.com/files/firepot1.jpg">Firepot: Cabilis</a>
<li><a href="http://www.everlore.com/ShowScreenShot.asp?image=http://www.everlore.com/files/firepot2.jpg">Firepot: Kaladim</a>
<li><a href="http://www.everlore.com/ShowScreenShot.asp?image=http://www.everlore.com/files/firepot3.jpg">Firepot: Ak'anon</a>
<li><a href="http://www.everlore.com/ShowScreenShot.asp?image=http://www.everlore.com/files/firepot4.jpg">Firepot: Rivervale</a>
<li><a href="http://www.everlore.com/ShowScreenShot.asp?image=http://www.everlore.com/files/firepot5.jpg">Firepot: Grobb</a>
<li><a href="http://www.everlore.com/ShowScreenShot.asp?image=http://www.everlore.com/files/firepot6.jpg">Firepot: Oggok</a>
<li><a href="http://www.everlore.com/ShowScreenShot.asp?image=http://www.everlore.com/files/firepot7.jpg">Firepot: Erudin</a>
<li><a href="http://www.everlore.com/ShowScreenShot.asp?image=http://www.everlore.com/files/firepot8.jpg">Firepot: Neriak</a>
<li><a href="http://www.everlore.com/ShowScreenShot.asp?image=http://www.everlore.com/files/firepot9.jpg">Firepot: Kelethin</a>
<li><a href="http://www.everlore.com/ShowScreenShot.asp?image=http://www.everlore.com/files/firepot10.jpg">Firepot: Felwithe</a>
<li><a href="http://www.everlore.com/ShowScreenShot.asp?image=http://www.everlore.com/files/firepot11.jpg">Firepot: Halas</a>
<li><a href="http://www.everlore.com/ShowScreenShot.asp?image=http://www.everlore.com/files/firepotRoom1.jpg">Room Screenshot 1</a>
